{"data":[{"name":"92:1","price":"रात की क़सम, जब वह छा जाए।","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا يَغۡشَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6059,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-al-layli idhā yaghshā ","translations":["By the night","when","it covers","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-al-layli","idhā","yaghshā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,980],[2,980,1640],[3,1640,2775]]}},{"name":"92:2","price":"और दिन की क़सम, जब वह रौशन हो जाए!","arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ إِذَا تَجَلَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6060,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-nahāri idhā tajallā ","translations":["And the day","when","it shines in brightness","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-nahāri","idhā","tajallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2000],[2,2000,2570],[3,2570,3855]]}},{"name":"92:3","price":"तथा नर और मादा को पैदा करने की क़सम।","arabic":"وَمَا خَلَقَ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلۡأُنثَىٰٓ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6061,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā khalaqa al-dhakara wal-unthā ","translations":["And He Who","created","the male","and the female","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","khalaqa","al-dhakara","wal-unthā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1260],[3,1260,2170],[4,2170,4415]]}},{"name":"92:4","price":"निःसंदेह तुम्हारे प्रयास विविध हैं।[1]","arabic":"إِنَّ سَعۡيَكُمۡ لَشَتَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6062,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1. (1-4) इन आयतों का भावार्थ यह है कि जिस प्रकार रात-दिन तथा नर-मादा (स्त्री-पुरुष) भिन्न हैं, और उनके लक्षण और प्रभाव भी भिन्न हैं, इसी प्रकार मानवजाति (इनसान) के विश्वास, कर्म भी दो भिन्न प्रकार के हैं। और दोनों के प्रभाव और परिणाम भी विभिन्न हैं।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"inna saʿyakum lashattā ","translations":["Indeed","your efforts","(are) surely diverse","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","saʿyakum","lashattā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1290],[2,1290,2330],[3,2330,3655]]}},{"name":"92:5","price":"फिर जिसने (दान) दिया और (अवज्ञा से) बचा।","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَنۡ أَعۡطَىٰ وَٱتَّقَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6063,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-ammā man aʿṭā wa-ittaqā ","translations":["Then as for","(him) who","gives","and fears","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-ammā","man","aʿṭā","wa-ittaqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1740],[2,1740,2150],[3,2150,3050],[4,3050,4725]]}},{"name":"92:6","price":"और सबसे अच्छी बात को सत्य माना।","arabic":"وَصَدَّقَ بِٱلۡحُسۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6064,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"waṣaddaqa bil-ḥus'nā ","translations":["And believes","in the best","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["waṣaddaqa","bil-ḥus'nā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,2425]]}},{"name":"92:7","price":"तो निश्चय हम उसके लिए भलाई को आसान कर देंगे।","arabic":"فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ لِلۡيُسۡرَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6065,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fasanuyassiruhu lil'yus'rā ","translations":["Then We will ease him","towards [the] ease","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["fasanuyassiruhu","lil'yus'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1790],[2,1790,3725]]}},{"name":"92:8","price":"लेकिन वह (व्यक्ति) जिसने कंजूसी की और बेपरवाही बरती।","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۢ بَخِلَ وَٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6066,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ammā man bakhila wa-is'taghnā ","translations":["But as for","(him) who","withholds","and considers himself free from need","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ammā","man","bakhila","wa-is'taghnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1720],[2,1720,2630],[3,2630,3250],[4,3250,4555]]}},{"name":"92:9","price":"और सबसे अच्छी बात को झुठलाया।","arabic":"وَكَذَّبَ بِٱلۡحُسۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6067,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wakadhaba bil-ḥus'nā ","translations":["And denies","the best","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wakadhaba","bil-ḥus'nā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,2455]]}},{"name":"92:10","price":"तो हम उसके लिए कठिनाई (बुराई का मार्ग) आसान कर देंगे।[2]","arabic":"فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ لِلۡعُسۡرَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6068,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2. (5-10) इन आयतों में दोनों भिन्न कर्मों के प्रभाव का वर्णन है कि कोई अपना धन भलाई में लगाता है तथा अल्लाह से डरता है और भलाई को मानता है। सत्य आस्था, स्वभाव और सत्कर्म का पालन करता है। जिसका प्रभाव यह होता है कि अल्लाह उसके लिए सत्कर्मों का मार्ग सरल कर देता है। और उसमें पाप करने तथा स्वार्थ के लिए अवैध धन अर्जन की भावना नहीं रह जाती। ऐसे व्यक्ति के लिए दोनों लोक में सुख है। दूसरा वह होता है जो धन का लोभी, तथा अल्लाह से निश्न्तचिंत होता है और भलाई को नहीं मानता। जिसका प्रभाव यह होता है कि उसका स्वभाव ऐसा बन जाता है कि उसे बुराई का मार्ग सरल लगने लगता है। तथा अपने स्वार्थ और मनोकामना की पूर्ति के लिए प्रयास करता है। फिर इस बात को इस वाक्य पर समाप्त कर दिया गया है कि धन के लिए वह जान देता है, परंतु वह उसे अपने साथ लेकर नहीं जाएगा। फिर वह उसके किस काम आएगा?","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fasanuyassiruhu lil'ʿus'rā ","translations":["Then We will ease him","towards [the] difficulty","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fasanuyassiruhu","lil'ʿus'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1760],[2,1760,3555]]}},{"name":"92:11","price":"और जब वह (जहन्नम के गड्ढे में) गिरेगा, तो उसका धन उसके किसी काम नहीं आएगा।","arabic":"وَمَا يُغۡنِي عَنۡهُ مَالُهُۥٓ إِذَا تَرَدَّىٰٓ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6069,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā yugh'nī ʿanhu māluhu idhā taraddā ","translations":["And not","will avail","him","his wealth","when","he falls","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","yugh'nī","ʿanhu","māluhu","idhā","taraddā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1540],[3,1540,2130],[4,2130,4670],[5,4670,5280],[6,5280,6595]]}},{"name":"92:12","price":"निःसंदेह हमारा ही ज़िम्मे मार्ग दिखाना है।","arabic":"إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا لَلۡهُدَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6070,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"inna ʿalaynā lalhudā ","translations":["Indeed","upon Us","(is) the guidance","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","ʿalaynā","lalhudā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1080],[2,1080,2250],[3,2250,3435]]}},{"name":"92:13","price":"निःसंदेह हमारे ही अधिकार में आख़िरत और दुनिया है।","arabic":"وَإِنَّ لَنَا لَلۡأٓخِرَةَ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6071,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-inna lanā lalākhirata wal-ūlā ","translations":["And indeed","for Us","(is) the Hereafter","and the first (life)","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-inna","lanā","lalākhirata","wal-ūlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1360],[2,1360,2110],[3,2110,3550],[4,3550,5025]]}},{"name":"92:14","price":"अतः मैंने तुम्हें भड़कती आग से सावधान कर दिया है।[3]","arabic":"فَأَنذَرۡتُكُمۡ نَارٗا تَلَظَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6072,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"3. (11-14) इन आयतों में मानवजाति (इनसान) को सावधान किया गया है कि अल्लाह का, दया और न्याय के कारण मात्र यह दायित्व था कि सत्य मार्ग दिखा दे। और क़ुरआन द्वारा उसने अपना यह दायित्व पूरा कर दिया। किसी को सत्य मार्ग पर लगा देना उसका दायित्व नहीं है। अब इस सीधी राह को अपनाओगे तो तुम्हारा ही भला होगा। अन्यथा याद रखो कि संसार और परलोक दोनों ही अल्लाह के अधिकार में हैं। न यहाँ कोई तुम्हें बचा सकता है, और न वहाँ कोई तुम्हारा सहायक होगा।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-andhartukum nāran talaẓẓā ","translations":["So I warn you","(of) a Fire","blazing","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-andhartukum","nāran","talaẓẓā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2650],[2,2650,4010],[3,4010,5555]]}},{"name":"92:15","price":"जिसमें केवल सबसे बड़ा अभागा ही प्रवेश करेगा।","arabic":"لَا يَصۡلَىٰهَآ إِلَّا ٱلۡأَشۡقَى","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6073,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"lā yaṣlāhā illā al-ashqā ","translations":["Not","will burn (in) it","except","the most wretched","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","yaṣlāhā","illā","al-ashqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,470],[2,470,3279],[3,3279,3899],[4,3899,5524]]}},{"name":"92:16","price":"जिसने झुठलाया तथा मुँह फेरा।","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6074,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī kadhaba watawallā ","translations":["The one who","denied","and turned away","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","kadhaba","watawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,2000],[3,2000,3405]]}},{"name":"92:17","price":"और उससे उस व्यक्ति को बचा लिया जाएगा, जो सबसे ज़्यादा परहेज़गार है।","arabic":"وَسَيُجَنَّبُهَا ٱلۡأَتۡقَى","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6075,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wasayujannabuhā al-atqā ","translations":["But will be removed from it","the righteous","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["wasayujannabuhā","al-atqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,3040],[2,3040,4585]]}},{"name":"92:18","price":"जो अपना धन देता है, ताकि वह पवित्र हो जाए।","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يُؤۡتِي مَالَهُۥ يَتَزَكَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6076,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī yu'tī mālahu yatazakkā ","translations":["The one who","gives","his wealth","(to) purify himself","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","yu'tī","mālahu","yatazakkā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1090],[2,1090,1890],[3,1890,3000],[4,3000,4515]]}},{"name":"92:19","price":"और उसपर किसी का कोई उपकार नहीं है, जिसका बदला चुकाया जाए।","arabic":"وَمَا لِأَحَدٍ عِندَهُۥ مِن نِّعۡمَةٖ تُجۡزَىٰٓ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6077,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā li-aḥadin ʿindahu min niʿ'matin tuj'zā ","translations":["And not","for anyone","with him","any","favor","to be recompensed","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","li-aḥadin","ʿindahu","min","niʿ'matin","tuj'zā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1650],[3,1650,3320],[4,3320,3620],[5,3620,6310],[6,6310,7405]]}},{"name":"92:20","price":"वह तो केवल अपने सर्वोच्च रब का चेहरा चाहता है।","arabic":"إِلَّا ٱبۡتِغَآءَ وَجۡهِ رَبِّهِ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6078,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"illā ib'tighāa wajhi rabbihi al-aʿlā ","translations":["Except","seeking","(the) Countenance","(of) his Lord","the Most High","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","ib'tighāa","wajhi","rabbihi","al-aʿlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,600],[2,600,3409],[3,3409,3969],[4,3969,4879],[5,4879,6054]]}},{"name":"92:21","price":"और निश्चय वह (बंदा) प्रसन्न हो जाएगा।[4]","arabic":"وَلَسَوۡفَ يَرۡضَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6079,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"4. (15-21) इन आयतों में यह वर्णन किया गया है कि कौन से कुकर्मी नरक में पड़ेंगे और कौन सुकर्मी उससे सुरक्षित रखे जाएँगे। और उन्हें क्या फल मिलेगा। आयत संख्या 10 के बारे में यह बात याद रखने की है कि अल्लाह ने सभी वस्तुओं और कर्मों का अपने नियमानुसार स्वभाविक प्रभाव रखा है। और क़ुरआन इसीलिए सभी कर्मों के स्वभाविक प्रभाव और फल को अल्लाह से जोड़ता है। और यूँ कहता है कि अल्लाह ने उसके लिए बुराई की राह सरल कर दी। कभी कहता है कि उनके दिलों पर मुहर लगा दी, जिसका अर्थ यह होता है कि यह अल्लाह के बनाए हुए नियमों के विरोध का स्वभाविक फल है। (देखिए : उम्मुल किताब, मौलाना आज़ाद)","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"walasawfa yarḍā ","translations":["And soon, surely","he will be pleased","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["walasawfa","yarḍā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1240],[2,1240,2285]]}}],"chapter":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail","Chapter Al-Lail","Lail","Surah Lail","Chapter Lail","Al Lail","Surah Al Lail","Chapter Al Lail","Surah 92","Chapter 92","The Night","الليل"],"version":{"key":"hindi_omari","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"hi","version":"1.1.4","last_update":1675069101,"title":"Hindi Translation","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Indian by Azizul-Haqq Al-Umary."}}